 system\nbased on this inviscid Voigt regularization. Finally, we propose a\nVoigt-$\\alpha$ regularization for the inviscid 3D Boussinesq equations with\ndiffusion, and prove its global well-posedness. It is worth mentioning that our\nresults are also valid in the presence of the $\\beta$-plane approximation of\nthe Coriolis force.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Oct 2010 00:08:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-10-26"}
