gue that Xe-based experiments may provide\nthe best case for a 1-ton scale experiment, given the potentially very low\nbackgrounds achievable and the expected scalability to large isotope masses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Oct 2010 13:18:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Nov 2010 15:44:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 14 Dec 2010 18:40:56 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2011 10:47:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-06-09"}
